title: Fictional Women Around the World: Dana Scully
itunes:title: Fictional Women Around the World: Dana Scully
description:
Skeptic. Inspiration. Fashion icon. After her run on the The X-Files,  Dana Scully got not one but two effects named after her. We investigate the background and impact of this character. And the pants suits. Oh the pants suits.
